item.description:
@Sepranem wrote:

  1. Server is offline.
  2. Server’s coding is bugged.
  3. Server’s host hasn’t port-forwarded.
  4. Server’s host gave incorrect information.
  5. Server is full.
  6. You are banned from the server.

Could be any one of those.
